Title: Digging Up The Same Old Ground
Presenters: Sean M. Davis, Ferrett Steinmetz, NIcole Castle
Book Description: 'Are there any new stories left- or is everything just a retread of an old idea?  What is a retread- and what is a legitimately new angle?'

Title: Apocalypse When?
Book Description: 'Zombies- mutant viruses- alien invaders- kaiju- or the environment- the end of the world is a mainstay of science fiction.  What type of apocalypse do we enjoy exploring?  Come here for all of your dystopian needs.'
